name: Lepus Nava #01
description:
The 'Lepus Nava' is one of many kinds who have a duty to protect the newborn star. Their job is to travel through universes, dimensions, and time. Find a newborn weak star that doesn't have a gardien, protect it till it grows strong with enough power to protect itself from 'Orion', the star hunter.
